name: H5D
description: H5D launched the Dao organization token for Heliin wireless network equipment manufacturer, aiming to properly distribute wireless network data fuel machines and effectively subscribe to Helium wireless devices. It is issued as a proof of network coverage and transmission volume, as well as for fundraising purposes. The initial issuance price is 1 USD, with stable growth in transmission and fundraising volume. It is the most powerful Dao stock return token in the 5G+era.
